column2: 1. Runs must keep a kill/score ratio of 2.5 kills per 100k
2. Runs obtained with a perviously nerfed tank will be placed onto the 'Legacy Runs' section
3. It is recommended that you record your runs and upload them to youtube, but this is not required
4. If you recorded your gameplay, your time stops as soon as you reach the milestone (1m, 2m, 3m)
However, if you did not record your time will be counted as what is on your death screen
5. Runs abusing any sort of bug, glitch, or any unlegit means (feeding, teaming, etc.) will be rejected.
